1
00:00:06,639 --> 00:00:07,307
This place is tiny.

2
00:00:07,308 --> 00:00:08,708
How are we supposed to rest here?

3
00:00:09,109 --> 00:00:10,109
Go take care of it, now.

4
00:00:10,443 --> 00:00:12,078
Fine, I'll go ask.

5
00:00:16,616 --> 00:00:17,616
I'm gonna look around.

6
00:00:28,428 --> 00:00:29,729
Sorry.

7
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:31,964
It was an accident.

8
00:00:31,965 --> 00:00:33,600
You don't have to look so pissed.

9
00:00:35,001 --> 00:00:36,001
I'm not.

10
00:00:36,236 --> 00:00:38,171
I just don't like being touched.

11
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,773
You don't like being touched?

12
00:00:40,774 --> 00:00:41,908
Then why wont you let go?

13
00:00:51,057 --> 00:00:52,825
A "Black and White" showdown?

14
00:00:57,375 --> 00:00:58,199
[Their clothes are too similar, is Bai Xing ripping him off?]

15
00:00:58,224 --> 00:00:59,793
Who's even copying who?

16
00:00:59,826 --> 00:01:00,196
[Why's he wearing all white? Is he trying to copy our style?]

17
00:01:00,221 --> 00:01:01,995
Like I'd ever want to copy his look.

18
00:01:10,670 --> 00:01:11,304
Xiaoan said

19
00:01:11,305 --> 00:01:12,504
you shouldn't be telling the fans

20
00:01:12,505 --> 00:01:13,706
about all this drama.

21
00:01:14,207 --> 00:01:15,108
Come on,

22
00:01:15,109 --> 00:01:16,776
I can't just let them talk trash.

23
00:01:17,277 --> 00:01:18,178
People are actually saying

24
00:01:18,179 --> 00:01:19,646
I'm ripping off his songs.

25
00:01:20,580 --> 00:01:21,448
It's ridiculous.

26
00:01:21,448 --> 00:01:21,948
Alright, alright.

27
00:01:21,948 --> 00:01:22,682
Let's just head inside.

28
00:01:22,682 --> 00:01:23,682
Come on, let's go.

29
00:01:28,388 --> 00:01:29,022
Excuse me.

30
00:01:29,023 --> 00:01:30,123
Sorry, coming through.

31
00:01:35,562 --> 00:01:37,063
You're the one leaking those rumors.

32
00:01:38,031 --> 00:01:39,732
Drama is what builds hype.

33
00:01:41,835 --> 00:01:43,268
Can't people just rely on talent?

34
00:01:43,269 --> 00:01:44,604
Why does it have to be like this?

35
00:01:46,005 --> 00:01:47,973
When you first signed with me,

36
00:01:47,974 --> 00:01:48,942
didn't you say you wanted to prove yourself

37
00:01:48,943 --> 00:01:50,876
to that person you have a crush on?

38
00:01:50,877 --> 00:01:52,512
To show them what you're capable of?

39
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:55,782
Talent alone doesn't cut it anymore.

40
00:01:56,483 --> 00:01:57,550
Don't be naive.

41
00:01:58,384 --> 00:01:59,285
Trust me.

42
00:01:59,286 --> 00:02:00,487
I've got your back.

43
00:02:01,821 --> 00:02:03,821
Now, there's one more
appearance you need to make.
